<p>
    <strong>What is a bot?</strong>
    A bot is a software robot or a malware instance that runs autonomously on a compromised machine, often without being noticed by the victim user
    <button type="button"
            class="btn btn-sm reference"
            data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="right"
