        [50].
    </button>
</p>

<p>
    <strong>A Botnet</strong>, also referred to as a <em>zombie army</em>,
    is the root cause of a large number of security problems on the internet; capable of large scale spamming, DDos attacks, data theft and fraud. A study shows that, on a typical day, about 40% of the 800 million computers connected to the Internet are in a botnet

