</p>

<p>
    <strong>Why do people create botnets?</strong>
<ul>
    <li>To profit financially</li>
    <li>To make a political or social statement</li>
    <li>To establish a name for themselves in the hacker community</li>
    <li>To celebrate some person or event</li>
    <li>To show companies how their systems are flawed</li>
    <li>Just because they can</li>

